{"type": "article", "id": 20162, "title": "分离式台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-04T07:40:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130451D2XeOtzPx3J5UwkM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款外形很普通的灯，但灯的底座和灯罩是分离的。将底座固定之后，这盏灯的灯罩就可以 360°转动，来改变光的方向。灯的底座是一块圆盘带一根圆柱，用大理石或混凝土做的，显得厚重。可以搭配以黄铜等材料的灯罩，直接插在圆柱上，轻盈而富有色彩的变化。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150404XTbamBcdvOxHIlMq.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"664\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150404q1MiNdOa7LzeHCAG.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"695\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261504052royOcJxHtDYIZik.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"737\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261504052tGN6Y35gPZI8mkp.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"714\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}